window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Kaiden might be a genius when it comes to destruction, but the other side has the greatest warship on the planet.</b></p> <p>It's about even. Kaiden, plus the rest of the academy students and faculty, are working to take down the AO's greatest threat: the <i>City-Killer</i>. Will they be able to destroy the ship that forced them from their homes? If they do, what will be the cost?</p> <p>Includes a special note from the author.</p>"; 
